{"tid":778666,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【河馬「殺」人】中國使館厚顏邀功 遇事台人「救星」係佢！","createTime":"2018-08-14T01:03:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T02:00:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4b443a14985a4d02e39944b4edfa03414bece75b","tid":778666,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T01:03:58.000Z","msg":"一個台灣旅行團上周六在肯雅遊玩期間，有兩名團友遭河馬襲擊，導致1死1傷；同團團友隨後又遇上車禍，致約15人受傷。中國官媒新華社事後宣稱，中國駐肯雅大使館高度關注此事，並表示會作出積極協助，卻被踢爆根本是在「厚顏邀功」。真正協助遇事台灣旅行團的，其實是在東非有台灣「民間大使」之稱的前僑務委員陳發。<br />\n<br />\n據台灣《蘋果》報道，自台灣遊客在肯雅發生意外的消息傳出後，新華社在相關報道中吹噓，中國駐肯雅大使館高度關注此事，「第一時間」就派使館官員到現場了解，中國駐肯雅使館還說「將同肯亞政府相關部門密切配合，為遇難者遺體出境、傷者治療和善後處理等事宜提供積極協助」。此一消息讓外界以為都是中國官員在處理善後。<br />\n<br />\n不過，在肯雅當地專辦非洲團的左右旅遊負責人施聖亭，在接受台灣《蘋果》訪問時表示，事發當天聯絡各界資源幫忙、協助繙譯、協助重傷者轉大醫院接受治療，以及協調肯雅航空安排航班機位、協助遇難者遺體出境等，全都是73歲的陳發出錢出力義務幫忙。<br />\n<br />\n至於在車禍重傷的5名台灣人中，有一名傷者需要轉院治療，陳發也協助轉院，並親自隨車護送。施聖亭提供台灣遊客的傷勢資訊，包括段姓遊客鼻骨骨折、黃先生頭部挫傷，鄭先生手肘骨折，三人均需手術，但無生命危險。<br />\n<br />\n施聖亭表示，陳發過去是台灣在肯雅唯一的僑務委員，於今年5月卸任。每次有台灣人在東非出事，他扮演出「民間大使」，出錢出力義務幫忙。　<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/10793096/realtime/article/20180813/58558504\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2F10793096%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180813%2F58558504&d=WU70cn3kxO7zAgzGaBbBPYM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=45ff51f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2F10793096%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180813%2F58558504&h=b07dc575\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/10793096/realtime/article/20180813/58558504</a>"},{"pid":"3cdd05e8eba1acea5434a91201e6dcd0a50a1efe","tid":778666,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T01:06:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acfaeadc1c88bbd1471d0e02202874225275f495","tid":778666,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T01:08:49.000Z","msg":"支那又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4659b110ba292414643f3b74a0c3bf330835af5a","tid":778666,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T01:38:57.000Z","msg":"中國台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a21df872ac8a7a597d364e11ffdb0f08a3b7687","tid":778666,"uid":9899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T01:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c61d1f23817c1ed28651c1db5c2bc205307b46","tid":778666,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T01:56:54.000Z","msg":"咁佢真係好好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n垃圾支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0313f1721bcb83a08869d9cb1dc36a501d486df","tid":778666,"uid":13115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T01:58:39.000Z","msg":"小支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c9c738d0c3352fd221b2f8e3bdbe77b6ded950","tid":778666,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T02:00:23.000Z","msg":"台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}